# LaTeX manuscript build-artifacts. The pipeline writes table fragments
# (generated/results_*.tex) and \newcommand macro files (generated/macros*.tex)
# for the paper; those belong with the manuscript, not this code repo. Only the
# numerical *.csv outputs are tracked here. (This also covers the transient
# default-tier snapshot generated/.macros_default_snapshot.tex.)
generated/*.tex
